msgSnippet: ... assertEquals assumes that your equals implementation works. To test whether your equals implementation works, use something like GSBase s EqualsTester. J.
messageBody:
>So said Thomas SMETS on 2003-05-19 --------------------
>I am wondering why the assertEquals is not doing a more thorough
>validation.

assertEquals assumes that your equals implementation works. To test whether your equals implementation works, use something like GSBase's EqualsTester.
